query:
UPDATE assessments a
INNER JOIN building_components bc ON LOWER(TRIM(a.componentName)) = LOWER(TRIM(bc.name))
SET 
  a.uniformatId = bc.id,
  a.uniformatLevel = bc.level,
  a.uniformatGroup = SUBSTRING(bc.code, 1, 1)
WHERE a.uniformatId IS NULL 
  AND a.componentName IS NOT NULL 
  AND a.componentName != '';
